casebody.data:
The People of the State of New York v. William Hernandez.

Motion granted insofar as to extend the defendant’s time to serve and file the record on appeal and appellant’s points to and including February 2, 1960, with notice of argument for the March 1960 Term of this court, said appeal to be argued or submitted when reached. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, M. M. Frank, Yalente and Stevens, JJ.
